{"id":599840,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/【异闻观止】影星接力中国，一点不能少/","date":"2018-11-18T17:26:34Z","modified":"2018-11-18T19:51:28Z","title":"【异闻观止】影星接力“中国，一点不能少”","content":"<p><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">编者按：第55届金马奖颁奖典礼上，获得最佳纪录片奖的台湾导演傅榆在获奖感言中称，“表示希望有一天我们的国家可以被当成真正独立的个体来看待，这是我生为台湾人最大的愿望。” 她的言论在大陆激起强烈反响，</span>《人民日报》、共青团等官方媒体和机构立刻在微博刊登“中国一点都不能少”来表明立场。影星范冰冰在税务问题后首次发文，转发她转发共青团中央微博并写道：中国，一点都不能少，徐峥、胡歌、黄晓明、邓超等影星也纷纷转发他们的微博以表明自己的立场。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-599842\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture1-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"196\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture1-2.png 678w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture1-2-300x118.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-599843\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture2-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture2-1.png 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture2-1-300x213.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-599844\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/1-32.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"252\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/1-32.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/1-32-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-599845\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/2-29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/2-29.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/2-29-300x203.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-599846\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/file